\c 1
\s Ukuzalwa kukaSamuweli
\p
\v 1 Kwakukhona-ke indoda ethile yeRamathayimi-Zofimu entabeni yakoEfrayimi\x + Josh. 24.33.\x*; lebizo layo lalinguElkana indodana kaJerohamu, indodana kaElihu, indodana kaTohu, indodana kaZufi\x + 1 Lan. 6.22,26,27,34,35.\x* umEfrayimi\x + Gen. 35.19.\x*.
\v 2 Njalo yayilabafazi ababili; ibizo lomunye lalinguHana, lebizo lomunye lalinguPenina. Njalo uPenina wayelabantwana, kodwa uHana wayengelabantwana\x + Hlu. 13.2. Luka 1.7.\x*.
\v 3 Leyondoda yenyuka-ke isuka emzini wayo iminyaka ngeminyaka\x + Eks. 23.14. Luka 2.41.\x* ukuyakhonza lokuhlabela iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla\x + Dute. 12.5,6,7.\x* eShilo\x + Josh. 18.1.\x*, njalo kwakukhona lapho amadodana amabili kaEli, uHofini loPhinehasi, abapristi beN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 4 Kwakusithi mhla uElkana ehlaba, wanika uPenina umkakhe lawo wonke amadodana akhe lamadodakazi akhe izabelo;
\v 5 kodwa uHana wamnika isabelo esiphindwe kabili, ngoba wayemthanda uHana; kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* yayisivalile isizalo sakhe\x + Dute. 12.17,18. 16.11.\x*.
\v 6 Lesitha sakhe laso samcaphula ngentukuthelo ukuze simkhathaze, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yayisivalile isizalo sakhe\x + Jobe 24.21.\x*.
\v 7 Wayesenza njalo-ke iminyaka ngeminyaka; kusukela lapho esenyukela endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*, ngokunjalo samcaphula. Ngakho walila, kadlanga.
\v 8 UElkana umkakhe wasesithi kuye: Hana, ulilelani? Njalo kawudli ngani? Kungani-ke inhliziyo yakho idabukile? Mina kangingcono kuwe kulamadodana alitshumi yini\x + Ruthe 4.15.\x*?
\p
\v 9 Ngakho uHana wasukuma emva kokudla eShilo\x + Josh. 18.1.\x* langemva kokunatha. UEli umpristi wayehlezi-ke esihlalweni phansi kwensika yethempeli leN\nd kosi\x + 3.3.\x*\nd*.
\v 10 Njalo wayelobuhlungu emphefumulweni, wasekhuleka eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ekhala lokukhala inyembezi\x + Jobe 7.11. 10.1.\x*.
\v 11 Wasefunga isifungo\x + Hlu. 11.30.\x* wathi: N\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, uba ungabona lokubona ukuhlupheka kwencekukazi yakho\x + Gen. 29.32. 2 Sam. 16.12.\x*, ungikhumbule, ungakhohlwa incekukazi yakho, kodwa unike incekukazi yakho inzalo yesilisa, ngizamnika iN\nd kosi\nd* insuku zonke zempilo yakhe\x + 1.19. Gen. 8.1.\x*, lempuco kayiyikwedlula ekhanda lakhe\x + Hlu. 13.5.\x*.
\v 12 Kwasekusithi esaqhubeka ukukhuleka phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, uEli waqaphelisa umlomo wakhe.
\v 13 UHana wayekhulumela-ke enhliziyweni yakhe, kwanyikinyeka indebe zakhe kuphela, kodwa ilizwi lakhe lalingezwakali; ngakho uEli wacabanga ukuthi udakiwe.
\v 14 UEli wasesithi kuye: Koze kube nini udakwa? Susa iwayini lakho kuwe.
\v 15 UHana wasephendula wathi: Hatshi, nkosi yami, ngingowesifazana odabukileyo emoyeni; kanginathanga wayini loba okunathwayo okulamandla, kodwa bengithulula umphefumulo wami phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + Jobe 30.16. Hlab. 42.4. Hlab. 62.8. Lilo 2.19.\x*\nd*.
\v 16 Ungayithathi incekukazi yakho njengendodakazi kaBheliyali\x + Dute. 13.13. 15.9.\x*, ngoba ebunengini bosizi lwami lenkathazo yami sengikhulume kwaze kwaba khathesi.
\v 17 UEli wasephendula wathi: Hamba ngokuthula\x + 25.35. 20.13,42. 2 Sam. 15.9. 2 Kho. 5.19. Mark. 5.34. Luka 7.50. 8.48.\x*; uNkulunkulu wakoIsrayeli a\add ku\add*nike isicelo sakho osicele kuye\x + Hlab. 20.4,5.\x*.
\v 18 Wasesithi: Incekukazi yakho kayithole umusa emehlweni akho\x + Gen. 33.15.\x*. Ngakho owesifazana wahamba ngendlela yakhe, wadla; lobuso bakhe abaze busa\add nyukumala\add* ngakho\x + Tshu. 9.7.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Basebevuka ekuseni kakhulu, bakhonza phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, basebebuyela bafika emzini wabo eRama\x + 1.1. 2.11. 7.17. 8.4. 15.34. 16.13. 19.18,19,22,23. 20.1. 25.1. 28.3. 9.16. Mat. 27.57.\x*. UElkana wasemazi uHana umkakhe, leN\nd kosi\nd* yamkhumbula\x + 1.11.\x*.
\v 20 Kwasekusithi ekuqhubekeni kwesikhathi uHana wakhulelwa, wabeletha indodana, wayitha ibizo layo uSamuweli; ngoba \add wathi\add*: Ngimcelile eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Eks. 18.4.\x*.
\v 21 Lendoda uElkana lendlu yakhe yonke benyukela ukuyahlabela iN\nd kosi\nd* umhlatshelo weminyaka ngeminyaka, lesifungo sakhe\x + 1.3.\x*.
\v 22 Kodwa uHana kenyukanga, ngoba wathi kumkakhe: \add Kangiyikuhamba\add* aze alunyulwe umfana; khona ngizamletha ukuze abonakale phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, abesehlala khona kuze kube nininini\x + 1.11,28. 2.11,18. 3.1. Eks. 21.6. 2 Sam. 7.29.\x*.
\v 23 UElkana umkakhe wasesithi kuye: Yenza okulungileyo emehlweni akho; hlala uze umlumule\x + Nani 30.7.\x*; kuphela, iN\nd kosi\nd* kayiqinise ilizwi lakho\x + 2 Sam. 7.25.\x*. Ngokunjalo owesifazana wahlala, wayimunyisa indodana yakhe waze wayilumula.
\p
\v 24 Wasesenyuka layo eseyilumule, elamajongosi amathathu, \w le-efa\w** elilodwa lempuphu, lembodlela yewayini\x + Dute. 12.5,6,11.\x*, wayiletha endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd* eShilo\x + 1.3,9. Josh. 18.1.\x*; lomfana wayemncinyane.
\v 25 Balihlaba ijongosi, bamletha umntwana kuEli.
\v 26 Wasesithi: Hawu nkosi yami, kuphila komphefumulo wakho, nkosi yami, yimi owesifazana owayemi lawe lapha, ekhuleka eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 17.55. 20.3. Gen. 42.15. 2 Kho. 2.2,4,6. 4.30.\x*.
\v 27 Ngakhulekela lo umfana, njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* inginikile isicelo sami engasicela kuyo\x + 1.17.\x*.
\v 28 Ngakho lami ngimnikele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, zonke izinsuku ekhona; wacelwa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 1.11,22.\x*. Wasekhonza iN\nd kosi\nd* lapho\x + Gen. 24.26,52.\x*.